<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>833</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ de gōng yì rú guāng huī fā chū, zhǔ de jiù ēn yǐ chuán biàn sì fāng.
 liè guó jǐ kàn dào shén de zuò wèi, liè wáng yǐ kàn jiàn tā de róng guāng.
 shì shàng suǒ yǒu de gē shǒu dōu yào xiàng shén lái gē chàng.
 liè guó de lè qì dōu yào zàn měi sòng yáng.
 yīn wèi yé hé huá zài quán de zuò wáng, zài quán de zuò wáng.
 la la, yé hé huá zài quán de zuò wáng.</lyrics>
<title>yé hé huá zài quán de zuò wáng 迦南833</title>
</song>